.TH "call_netdevice_notifiers_mtu" 9 "call_netdevice_notifiers_mtu" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
call_netdevice_notifiers_mtu \- call all network notifier blocks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" call_netdevice_notifiers_mtu
.BI "(unsigned long val "  ","
.BI "struct net_device *dev "  ","
.BI "u32 arg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "val" 12
value passed unmodified to notifier function
.IP "dev" 12
net_device pointer passed unmodified to notifier function
.IP "arg" 12
additional u32 argument passed to the notifier function

Call all network notifier blocks.  Parameters and return value
are as for \fBraw_notifier_call_chain\fP.
